      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an AI agent designed to identify Partner Companies for a specific product: **Acumatica**.\n\nContext Data for the target company:\n- Website: {{ $json[\"COMPANY WEBSITE\"] }}\n- LinkedIn URL: {{ $json[\"LINKEDIN URL\"] }}\n\nAnalyze the provided LinkedIn and/or website content and determine whether the company is a Partner for Acumatica.\n\nInstructions:\n1. Search the About section on LinkedIn or the Company Website for any mention of \"Acumatica\".\n2. If the product name appears, confirm the company as a Partner.\n3. Always include the company's LinkedIn URL and Website in your output - even if empty or not mentioned.\n4. If no mention of \"Acumatica\" is found, return Partner Confirmation: No.\n\nOutput must always follow this exact format:\n\nPartner Confirmation: [Yes/No]\nReasoning: [Provide a brief 1-2 sentence explanation of where the confirmation was found or why it failed]",
